<h1>Statement of Claim (Particulars)</h1>

<p><strong>Claimant (Pursuer):</strong> {{landlord_full_name}}</p>
<p><strong>Respondent (Defender):</strong> {{tenant_full_name}}</p>
<p><strong>Property:</strong> {{property_address}}</p>
<p><strong>Sheriff Court:</strong> {{sheriffdom}}</p>

<h2>Background to the claim</h2>
<p>
  The Defender occupies the above property under a private residential tenancy that commenced on
  {{tenancy_start_date}}. The agreed rent is {{currency rent_amount}} per {{rent_frequency}}, payable in advance on
  the {{payment_day}} of each period.
</p>

<h2>Rent arrears</h2>
<p>
  The Defender has failed to pay rent as it fell due under the tenancy agreement. As at {{generation_date}},
  the outstanding arrears amount to {{currency arrears_total}}. A detailed schedule showing the arrears for each
  rent period is attached and forms part of this claim (marked "Schedule of Rent Arrears").
</p>

<h2>Property damage and other sums</h2>
{{#if damage_items.length}}
<p>The Defender caused damage to the property beyond normal wear and tear. The Pursuer claims the following sums for repairs and reinstatement:</p>
<ul>
  {{#each damage_items}}
  <li>{{description}} – {{currency amount}}</li>
  {{/each}}
</ul>
{{/if}}

{{#if other_charges.length}}
<p>The Pursuer also claims the following additional sums which are reasonably due:</p>
<ul>
  {{#each other_charges}}
  <li>{{description}} – {{currency amount}}</li>
  {{/each}}
</ul>
{{/if}}

<h2>Attempts to resolve the dispute</h2>
<p>
  {{#if attempts_to_resolve}}
  {{attempts_to_resolve}}
  {{else}}
  The Pursuer has made reasonable attempts to resolve this matter with the Defender before raising court proceedings.
  The Pursuer sent written demands for payment on {{demand_letter_date}} and {{second_demand_date}}, but the Defender
  has failed to make payment or engage meaningfully to resolve the debt.
  {{/if}}
</p>

<h2>Interest</h2>
<p>
  The Pursuer claims interest on the principal sum at the rate of {{interest_rate}}% per annum from {{interest_start_date}}
  to {{generation_date}}, calculated at {{currency interest_to_date}}, and continuing to accrue at {{currency daily_interest}}
  per day until payment is made in full.
</p>

<h2>Relief sought</h2>
<p>The Pursuer respectfully asks the Sheriff Court to grant decree for:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Payment of arrears, damages and other sums totalling {{currency total_claim_amount}}</li>
  <li>Court fee of {{currency court_fee}}</li>
  {{#if solicitor_costs}}
  <li>Legal expenses of {{currency solicitor_costs}}</li>
  {{/if}}
  <li>Interest as calculated above, continuing until payment</li>
</ol>

<h2>Statement of truth</h2>
<p>
  I confirm that the facts stated in this claim are true to the best of my knowledge and belief.
</p>
